plot: Toby and Michelle track a dangerous and highly-sophisticated gang, while feeling the pressure of a new, ambitious superintendent.

The armed robbery of an armored truck by five masked criminals with specially built armor-piercing bullets hits close to home with Michelle, who recognizes the slain cop from their days together at the police academy. As Toby helps her retain her shaken objectivity, a new police superintendent puts a lot of unneeded pressure on Alvin to solve the case quickly. Meanwhile, Oz deals with a reporter who visits the hospital emergency room on one if its most manic days.—statmanjeff
